    <item>
      <title>津巴布韦啤酒制造商未能以当地货币缴纳 5500 万美元税款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/-zwg-usd-zimbabwe-s-delta-loses-bid-to-pay-55-million-tax-in-local-currency</link>
      <description><![CDATA[津巴布韦啤酒制造商和可口可乐公司瓶装商 Delta Corp. 上诉失败，拒绝以当地货币缴纳 5500 万美元税款，该国最高法院命令该公司以美元缴纳。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/-zwg-usd-zimbabwe-s-delta-loses-bid-to-pay-55-million-tax-in-local-currency</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 07:29:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度计划每年吸引 1100 亿美元外商直接投资以促进经济发展</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/india-targets-110-billion-fdi-a-year-to-help-boost-economy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度政府投资促进机构的一位高级官员表示，印度计划将年度外国直接投资增加 50% 以上，以帮助促进经济增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/india-targets-110-billion-fdi-a-year-to-help-boost-economy</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 07:17:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>报道称，越南国家主席苏林被任命负责监督该党</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/vietnam-president-to-lam-assigned-to-oversee-the-party-media-lyqx5k5g</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据该网站的一份声明称，越南国家主席苏林暂时代行领导越南共产党中央委员会和政治局，而总书记阮富仲则优先治疗自己的健康。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/vietnam-president-to-lam-assigned-to-oversee-the-party-media-lyqx5k5g</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 06:57:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英美资源集团计划在经济复苏缓慢的情况下削减更多钻石产量</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/anglo-plans-to-cut-more-diamond-output-amid-slow-recovery</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于钻石行业持续面临需求疲软和库存过剩的困境，英美资源集团 (Anglo American Plc) 正考虑进一步削减钻石产量，而其铂金部门的利润则进一步下滑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/anglo-plans-to-cut-more-diamond-output-amid-slow-recovery</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 06:26:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>沃尔沃称卡车需求减弱，涨价有助于恢复</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/volvo-defends-margins-with-higher-prices-as-truck-cycle-softens</link>
      <description><![CDATA[沃尔沃汽车公司第二季度的盈利超出了预期，并在竞争对手发布悲观预测后给人带来了安慰，因为这家卡车制造商在主要市场放缓的情况下仍成功捍卫了自己的利润率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/volvo-defends-margins-with-higher-prices-as-truck-cycle-softens</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 05:33:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>ABB 报告称，由于自动化业务疲软，订单量下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/abb-posts-record-margin-on-data-center-demand-confirms-guidance</link>
      <description><![CDATA[ABB 有限公司报告各地区订单下降，原因是其自动化产品需求减弱抵消了电网业务的增长，导致其股价下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/abb-posts-record-margin-on-data-center-demand-confirms-guidance</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 05:29:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>沃尔沃汽车因中国电动汽车关税冲突调整销售前景</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/volvo-car-profit-jumps-on-firm-prices-ev-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于欧盟与中国在电动汽车行业支持问题上产生的贸易争端可能对其产生影响，沃尔沃汽车公司略微下调了今年的汽车销量预测。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/volvo-car-profit-jumps-on-firm-prices-ev-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 05:26:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>诺华因新重磅药物需求上升上调 2024 年利润预测</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/novartis-raises-2024-profit-forecast-on-demand-for-new-drugs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[诺华公司备受关注的前列腺癌药物 Pluvicto 在最新季度的销售表现令人失望，令这家瑞士制药公司上调的利润预期黯然失色。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/novartis-raises-2024-profit-forecast-on-demand-for-new-drugs</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 05:09:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
